column.Name: MaterialType
column.lookupquery: SELECT ComponentTypeID, ComponentDescription FROM pComponentType ORDER BY ComponentOrder

column.Name: MaterialTemplateID
column.lookupquery: SELECT MaterialTemplateID, MaterialTemplateName FROM pMaterialTemplate WHERE Active = 1 ORDER BY MaterialTemplateName

column.Name: IntroSeasonYearID
column.lookupquery: SELECT SeasonYearID, SeasonYear FROM vwx_SeasonYear_SEL WHERE Active = 1

column.Name: TACalTemplateId
column.lookupquery: SELECT TACalTemplateId, TACalTemplateName FROM pTACalTemplate WHERE SeasonYearId = ##ID## AND Active=1

column.Name: A
column.lookupquery: SELECT CustomKey, Custom FROM xCustom15 Where Active = 1 ORDER BY Custom

column.Name: UOM
column.lookupquery: SELECT UOM, UOMValue FROM UOM order by UOMSort

column.Name: CurrencyType
column.lookupquery: SELECT DISTINCT CurrencyType, CurrencyType as CurrencyTypeName FROM sExchangeRateItem WHERE CurrencyType IS NOT NULL ORDER BY CurrencyType

column.Name: P
column.lookupquery: SELECT CountryCode, CountryName FROM uCountry Where Active = 1 ORDER BY CountryName

column.Name: S
column.lookupquery: SELECT CustomKey, Custom FROM xCustom8 Where Active = 1 ORDER BY Custom
